Mengerti?  - Memesan!  Memesan!

00:14:19.649 --> 00:14:21.106
Aku.. aku minta maaf.

00:14:21.232 --> 00:14:22.232
Tolong lanjutkan..

00:14:23.065 --> 00:14:24.315
Dr D'Souza, katamu

00:14:24.440 --> 00:14:29.273
Dr Preesha sendiri
memberi mereka obat tidur.

00:14:29.482 --> 00:14:30.273
Ya.

00:14:36.711 --> 00:14:37.962
